---
title: Pork Bun Cha Rice Bowl for Dinner with a Pork Banh Mi Wrap for Lunch
description: Cook once, with a twist for lunch. Cook an amazing dinner as usual, then put a new twist on the recipe to create something different for lunch the next day! Serve up pork bun cha (Vietnamese meatballs) with pickled onion and veggies for dinner, then serve the leftover meatballs with coconut mayo and crunchy veggies in a wrap, banh mi-style, for lunch. Extra delicious!

